  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a010/23/2017 2:16PM CT (19:16 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.8-SupplierSKUImport\">Supplier\u00a0SKU Import</h2><p>We added a new import/export tool for Supplier SKUs so you can manage your Supplier SKUs in batches!</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.8-TicketStatusQRCode\">Ticket Status QR Code</h2><p>We fixed an issue that would\u00a0prevent QR codes from showing on printed receipts.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.8-BackorderingNewSerializedItems\">Backordering New Serialized Items</h2><p>We\u00a0updated the ticket item search logic to allow for backordering new serialized items from a ticket.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.8-AccountingJournal-OpenBeta\">Accounting Journal - Open Beta</h2><p>The accounting journal is now in open beta! See\u00a0the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://support.repairq.io/hc/en-us/articles/115000086113-Accounting-Journal-Entries-Overview\" rel=\"nofollow\">Accounting Journal Entries Overview</a>\u00a0for directions on how to use it.</p><p>\u00a0</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.8-QuickBooksOnlineIntegration-OpenBeta\">QuickBooks Online Integration - Open Beta</h2><p>The QuickBooks Online Integration is now in open beta! See the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://support.repairq.io/hc/en-us/articles/115001256973-Quickbooks-Online-Integration\" rel=\"nofollow\">QuickBooks Online Integration page</a>\u00a0for details on how to get started.</p>",
